originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    c.kind AS company_type,
    k.keyword AS movie_keyword,
    pi.info AS person_info
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_type c ON mc.company_type_id = c.id
JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
JOIN 
    person_info pi ON a.person_id = pi.person_id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000 AND
    k.keyword LIKE '%action%'
ORDER BY 
    a.name, t.production_year DESC
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("t3"."ACTOR_NAME", "t3"."ACTOR_NAME") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t3"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t3"."COMPANY_TYPE", "t3"."MOVIE_KEYWORD", "t3"."PERSON_INFO", "t3"."production_year"
FROM (SELECT "aka_name"."name" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t1"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "company_type"."kind" AS "COMPANY_TYPE", "t0"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "person_info"."info" AS "PERSON_INFO", "t1"."production_year"
FROM "company_type"
INNER JOIN ("cast_info" INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "person_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "person_info"."person_id") ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "keyword"
WHERE "keyword" LIKE '%action%') AS "t0" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t0"."id" = "s1"."keyword_id" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000) AS "t1" INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "t1"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id") ON "s1"."movie_id" = "t1"."id") ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "t1"."id") ON "company_type"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_type_id"
ORDER BY "aka_name"."name", "t1"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 100) AS "t3"
